 # Steps to change the directory from Desktop to downloads 
 
 Step 1: locate the .config directory in the /home/user_name
 Step 2: In .config directory there is a file called user-dirs.dirs, open this file
 Step 3: There is a path for the desktop directory, just change the path to downloads and save that
 Step 4: Now reboot your system and you will see the downloads directory on Desktop
 
